snippet.title: STAR SHREDDERS Remastered Promo Trailer
snippet.description:
We are excited to announce the launch of STAR SHREDDERS Remastered now on Steam! 🚀💫 

Thank you to all involved and hope you enjoy the new fresh start of our adventure! Any feedback would be appreciated greatly as we continue on to the next stage. 😃

Buy now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/764090/STAR_SHREDDERS/
